description: Dans le but d'améliorer la gestion durable de ses ressources forestières, la République du Congo s'est engagée en 2008 dans la négociation d'un Accord de partenariat volontaire (APV) pour l’application des réglementations forestières, la gouvernance et les échanges commerciaux (FLEGT en acronyme anglais pour Forest Law Enforcement, Governance and Trade) avec l'Union européenne. L'accord est entré officiellement en vigueur le 1.3.2013.Le Système de vérification de la légalité (SVL) de l'APV de la République du Congo est composé de six éléments dont un audit indépendant. Le précédent contrat étant arrivé à échéance en 2019, le présent marché vise à mobiliser un nouvel auditeur indépendant.

description: The project aims to build upon the existing network of 6 Special Environmental Protected Areas (SEPAs) of Türkiye in Muğla and Antalya provinces namely; Gökova Bay, Datça and Bozburun Peninsulas, Köyceğiz-Dalyan, Fethiye-Göcek, Patara and Kaş-Kekova SEPAs, introduce proven conservation approaches from Gökova Bay experience, create additional No Fishing Zones, Trawling and Purse-sein Prohibited Areas, and restore habitats and ecological services. Institutional capacity of End Recipient and relevant stakeholders for managing and establishing ecologically connected MPAs system will be increased and proper enforcement for threatened marine habitat along the Muğla and Antalya coasts will be implemented. Public awareness will be raised to support designation of new marine protected areas The new controlled zones and areas will be complementary to existing ones in terms of ecological connectivity and size, as well as patrolling coverage.
title: Restoring Marine Ecosystem Connectivity in South Western Turkiye with Network of Marine Protected Areas Boosting Climate Change Resilience

results.content: Support to the EU’s Bilateral Relations with Strategic Partners on Climate-related Policies and Investment

description: The overall objective of this action is to promote the effective implementation of the Paris Agreement in the context of economic recovery from the pandemic crisis.
